    "notes": [
      {
        "h3": { "en": "Feet point down", "zh": "支脚朝下" },
        "body": { "en": "The four bumpers are the machine's feet, mounted under the frame. Each screw runs up from below — through the bumper and into a drop-in T-nut in the bottom slot — so the heads tuck out of sight underneath.", "zh": "四个橡胶脚垫就是机器的支脚，装在框架底面。每颗螺栓自下而上穿过橡胶脚垫，拧进底部型材槽的船形螺母，螺栓头便藏在底面之下，看不见。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:140mm; top:100mm; width:78mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": { "en": "Use the screws that come with the bumpers", "zh": "用橡胶脚垫自带的螺栓" },
        "body": { "en": "Many bumpers ship with their own screws. If yours do, fit those — they're sized to match the bumper.", "zh": "很多橡胶脚垫出厂就自带螺栓。你买的若也配了螺栓，就用自带的，尺寸和橡胶脚垫正好配套。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:135mm; top:30mm; width:70mm;"
      }
    ],
    "bom": {
      "label": { "en": "Bill of materials", "zh": "物料清单" },
